title: Japan, Germany pledge to maintain free trade
description:
The leaders of Japan and Germany have pledged to pursue free trade in the face of rising protectionism. Shinzo Abe and Angela Merkel held talks in Tokyo on Monday, just days after a Japan-EU free trade deal went into force.
